  Kouhai (k≈çhai)
    Run tasks at periodic intervals

  Usage:
    kouhai [--interval n] [--stop] <cmd>
    kouhai  --help
    kouhai  --version

  Options:
    -s, --stop        stop on error
    -h, --help        display help information
    -v, --version     display version information
    -i, --interval n  set refresh interval [default: 1s]
